he locals aren’t talking. What is the community hiding? Was Becca hiding a secret? A secret that someone would be willing to kill for?<br><br><span>[image error]</span><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1468271452i/19685841.jpg" alt=" photo 539d2019-5553-44c5-b63a-ac74c207ff86_zps8vbjy9mk.jpg" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>SUMMIT LAKE is told in two voices- Becca’s in the months before her death- and, Kelsey’s in present day. In flashbacks we hear about- Becca’s college life. A life that may have left clues to Becca's last moments.<br><br>I first came upon this book for it's lovely cover...I am so glad I did. This is a new author to pay attention to...in my humble opinion.<br><br>Thanks NetGalley. :)<br><br><br></span>
